Date: Thu, 25 Jun 2026 15:54:48 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] fix(rfork): isolate seeds across parallel ranks

Include pipeline and expert parallel ranks in RFork seed identity, prefix optional ranks to avoid topology collisions, bypass RFork for dynamic EPLB, and document the compatibility boundaries.

Signed-off-by: yangsonglin13 <yangsonglin566@gmail.com>
